OmniScript Element Reference

This guide contains explanations of the different elements that can be added to an OmniScript, such as Omnistudio Data Mapper actions. Each element uses an extendable Lightning web component or customizable HTML template.

Aggregates (see Creating a Formula or Aggregate in an OmniScript)

Adding OmniScript Elements to an Upgraded Org
To use new elements after upgrading an org, add OmniScript elements to the OmniScript Element Type picklist.
